{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"8441","heading":"Strategy reports","label":"8441 Strategy reports","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/ch91/schIII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs8441","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Executive Documents","Delegation of a Reporting AuthorityMemorandum of President of the United States, , 75 F.R. 19533, provided:Apr. 7, 2010Memorandum for the Secretary of StateBy the authority vested in me as President by the Constitution and the laws of the United States, including , United States Code, I hereby delegate to you the functions and authority conferred upon the President by section 301 of the Enhanced Partnership with Pakistan Act of 2009, , to make the specified report to the Congress.section 301 of title 3Public Law 111–73You are authorized and directed to notify the appropriate congressional committees and publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.Barack Obama."],"amendments":["Delegation of a Reporting AuthorityMemorandum of President of the United States, , 75 F.R. 19533, provided:Apr. 7, 2010Memorandum for the Secretary of StateBy the authority vested in me as President by the Constitution and the laws of the United States, including , United States Code, I hereby delegate to you the functions and authority conferred upon the President by section 301 of the Enhanced Partnership with Pakistan Act of 2009, , to make the specified report to the Congress.section 301 of title 3Public Law 111–73You are authorized and directed to notify the appropriate congressional committees and publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.Barack Obama."],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Pakistan assistance strategy report","label":"a Pakistan assistance strategy report","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs8441%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs8441%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A description of the principal objectives of United States assistance to Pakistan to be provided under subchapter I of this chapter.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs8441%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A general description of the specific programs, projects, and activities designed to achieve the purposes of and the respective funding levels for such programs, projects, and activities for fiscal years 2010 through 2014.section 8411 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs8441%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A plan for program monitoring, operations research, and impact evaluation research for assistance authorized under subchapter I of this chapter.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s8441/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs8441%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"11